our girl?"}, {"start": 690.4, "end": 692.1800000000001, "text": " It was a pleasure to have you guys here."}, {"start": 692.1800000000001, "end": 694.5000000000001, "text": " Two rich histories coming together."}, {"start": 694.5000000000001, "end": 696.5000000000001, "text": " Between you and me, admit you're losing to Georgia."}, {"start": 696.5000000000001, "end": 698.8000000000001, "text": " We cannot admit we're losing to Georgia."}, {"start": 698.8000000000001, "end": 699.94, "text": " The magic is in the air."}, {"start": 699.94, "end": 701.46, "text": " The hope's in the air."}, {"start": 701.46, "end": 702.7, "text": " Check for us next week."}, {"start": 702.7, "end": 703.9200000000001, "text": " Yo, let me give this."}, {"start": 707.74, "end": 708.98, "text": " Hey, let's go IU."}, {"start": 711.6200000000001, "end": 712.46, "text": " IU."}, {"start": 714.94, "end": 715.7800000000001, "text": " Don't touch him, pal."}, {"start": 715.7800000000001, "end": 717.9000000000001, "text": " Stop, stop, stop, stop, stop."}, {"start": 717.9000000000001, "end": 718.74, "text": " We're good."}, {"start": 718.74, "end": 719.58, "text": " Give him my hat, give him my hat back."}, {"start": 719.58, "end": 720.4200000000001, "text": " That's right."}, {"start": 720.4200000000001, "end": 721.2600000000001, "text": " I didn't take your hat."}, {"start": 721.62, "end": 722.46, "text": " I didn't take your hat."}, {"start": 722.46, "end": 723.3, "text": " Who took my hat?"}, {"start": 723.3, "end": 724.12, "text": " Let's go, let's go."}, {"start": 724.12, "end": 724.96, "text": " Hold me back, bro."}, {"start": 724.96, "end": 725.8, "text": " Hold me back."}, {"start": 725.8, "end": 726.62, "text": " If you wanna keep running your mouth,"}, {"start": 726.62, "end": 727.7, "text": " I'm gonna beat the shit out of you."}, {"start": 727.7, "end": 728.86, "text": " Are you actually?"}, {"start": 728.86, "end": 729.8199999999999, "text": " I'm an IU guy."}, {"start": 729.819999