re before a million."}, {"start": 781.54, "end": 782.86, "text": " That's the true goal."}, {"start": 782.86, "end": 785.7, "text": " So please, from the bottom of my heart, help me out."}, {"start": 785.7, "end": 788.34, "text": " If not, it's okay, just keep watching, whatever."}, {"start": 788.34, "end": 791.46, "text": " But most importantly, this would not be possible"}, {"start": 791.46, "end": 794.54, "text": " without Scotty and all the other people helping us"}, {"start": 794.54, "end": 796.66, "text": " behind the scenes, like Donnie, Jack,"}, {"start": 796.66, "end": 797.9, "text": " whoever you wanna say."}, {"start": 797.9, "end": 799.26, "text": " Shout out to all the boys helping us,"}, {"start": 799.26, "end": 800.34, "text": " most importantly, Scotty."}, {"start": 800.34, "end": 802.34, "text": " But even more importantly than that,"}, {"start": 802.34, "end": 804.26, "text": " I just wanna thank God for this opportunity."}, {"start": 804.26, "end": 807.9, "text": " None of it is truly possible without Him."}, {"start": 807.9, "end": 810.9, "text": " I know I say that a lot, and sometimes I get hate for it,"}, {"start": 810.9, "end": 812.78, "text": " which, you know, sometimes I understand,"}, {"start": 812.78, "end": 815.42, "text": " sometimes I don't, but at the end of the day,"}, {"start": 815.42, "end": 817.9, "text": " none of it is possible without God."}, {"start": 817.9, "end": 820.14, "text": " If you truly believe in Him and pray"}, {"start": 820.14, "end": 822.78, "text": " about whatever you want and really focus"}, {"start": 822.78, "end": 824.78, "text": " on building a relationship with Him,"}, {"start": 824.78, "end": 825.86, "text": " anything is possible."}, {"start": 825.86, "end": 829.9399999999999, "text": " So remember, tonight, say your prayers, talk to God."}, {"start": 829.9399999999999, "end": 831.06, "text": " I guess we're gonna end the video,"}, {"start": 831.06, "end": 832.38, "text": " and I'll see you guys next wee